### 1.4 RoomVisualGenerator.cs — Vẽ Tilemap cho phòng

**File**: [RoomVisualGenerator.cs](file:///e:/%21FPT/7.SP26/PRU213/NoWayOut/Assets/Scripts/ProceduralGeneration/Components/RoomVisualGenerator.cs) (588 dòng)

Component được add vào mỗi Room GameObject, chịu trách nhiệm tạo visual.

#### Tạo Floor — [CreateAutoFilledFloor()](file:///e:/%21FPT/7.SP26/PRU213/NoWayOut/Assets/Scripts/ProceduralGeneration/Components/RoomVisualGenerator.cs#254-288):
```csharp
// Tạo Grid + Tilemap
// Fill sàn CHỈ phần interior (bỏ edges vì đó là tường)
for (int x = 1; x < tilesX - 1; x++)
    for (int y = 1; y < tilesY - 1; y++)
        tilemap.SetTile(pos, floorTiles[Random.Range(0, count)]);
```

#### Tạo Walls — [CreateAutoFilledWalls()](file:///e:/%21FPT/7.SP26/PRU213/NoWayOut/Assets/Scripts/ProceduralGeneration/Components/RoomVisualGenerator.cs#289-387):
- **Chỉ fill edges** (x=0, x=max, y=0, y=max)
- Có **collision** (TilemapCollider2D + CompositeCollider2D + static Rigidbody2D)
- **Skip wall tiles tại vị trí door** (cửa = lỗ trên tường)
- Chọn tile đúng góc: [GetWallTileForPosition()](file:///e:/%21FPT/7.SP26/PRU213/NoWayOut/Assets/Scripts/ProceduralGeneration/Components/RoomVisualGenerator.cs#388-412) — TopLeft, TopRight, Top, Bottom, Left, Right...

#### Tạo Doors — [GenerateDoorPrefabs()](file:///e:/%21FPT/7.SP26/PRU213/NoWayOut/Assets/Scripts/ProceduralGeneration/Components/RoomVisualGenerator.cs#413-487):
- Chỉ tạo door cho **hướng có room kết nối** (`activeDirections`)
- Instantiate door prefab → thêm [DoorTrigger](file:///e:/%21FPT/7.SP26/PRU213/NoWayOut/Assets/Scripts/ProceduralGeneration/Components/DoorTrigger.cs#13-447) component
- Configure [DoorTrigger](file:///e:/%21FPT/7.SP26/PRU213/NoWayOut/Assets/Scripts/ProceduralGeneration/Components/DoorTrigger.cs#13-447) với `currentRoom`, `targetRoom`, `doorDirection`
- `BoxCollider2D` bắt đầu `isTrigger = false` (door đóng = tường chắn)

