### 1.5 DoorTrigger.cs — Hệ thống cửa

**File**: [DoorTrigger.cs](file:///e:/%21FPT/7.SP26/PRU213/NoWayOut/Assets/Scripts/ProceduralGeneration/Components/DoorTrigger.cs) (448 dòng)

#### Cơ chế hoạt động:

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Closed: Khởi tạo
    Closed --> Open: Player trong range (4f)
    Open --> Closed: Player ra ngoài range
    Closed --> Locked: LockDoor()
    Locked --> Closed: UnlockDoor()
    
    note right of Open: isTrigger = true\n(player đi xuyên qua)
    note right of Closed: isTrigger = false\n(chặn player)
```

#### Chi tiết:
1. **Auto Open/Close**: Mỗi frame check khoảng cách player ↔ door. Nếu ≤ 4f → mở, > 4f → đóng
2. **Collider State**: 
   - Đóng: `isTrigger = false` → door là tường, chặn player
   - Mở: `isTrigger = true` → player đi qua → trigger [OnTriggerEnter2D](file:///e:/%21FPT/7.SP26/PRU213/NoWayOut/Assets/Scripts/ProceduralGeneration/Components/DoorTrigger.cs#191-208)
3. **Room Transition**: Khi player đi qua door mở → gọi `RoomTransitionManager.TransitionToRoom()`
4. **Animation**: Dùng `SetBool("isOpen", true/false)` thay vì Trigger
5. **Lock/Unlock**: Hỗ trợ khóa cửa cho boss fights

#### Auto-find rooms khi Play Mode:
```csharp
// Đi lên hierarchy: Door → Doors → Visuals → Room_Start_0_0
Transform current = transform.parent;
while (current != null) {
    foundRoom = dungeonManager.GetRoomByGameObject(current.gameObject);
    if (foundRoom != null) break;
    current = current.parent;
}
// Tìm targetRoom từ connectedRooms[doorDirection]
```

