## 5. 🎮 GameManager.cs — Quản lý trạng thái game

**File**: [GameManager.cs](file:///e:/%21FPT/7.SP26/PRU213/NoWayOut/Assets/Scripts/Core/GameManager.cs) (232 dòng)

**Singleton pattern** — `GameManager.Instance`

#### Event System:
```csharp
// 2 events chính:
event Action<int, int> OnLightFragmentCollected; // (current, total)
event Action OnAllLightFragmentsCollected;       // Khi đủ 3/3
```

#### Auto-create components trong Awake():
```csharp
// Tự tạo nếu chưa có:
LightFragmentUI      → hiện UI fragment
FlashOfTruthUI       → hiện UI cooldown
DungeonLightingManager → ánh sáng
MinimapManager       → minimap
LightingHotbarUI     → hotbar ánh sáng
```

#### CollectLightFragment():
```csharp
lightFragmentsCollected++;
OnLightFragmentCollected?.Invoke(current, total); // → DungeonLightingManager mở rộng light
if (collected >= total)
    OnAllLightFragmentsCollected?.Invoke();        // → FlashOfTruth unlock
```

#### RestartGame():
- Thử regenerate map với seed mới (MapInitializationManager hoặc legacy builder)
- Fallback: reload scene

